Package seng202.group5.information

Class Ingredient

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.group5.information.Ingredient
  • public class Ingredient
extends java.lang.Object
    The Ingredient class records all the base data for each ingredient in the database which include its name, price, category, id and its price.
